r />\n棒球係亞洲就好似關駐當地美軍事<br />\nNBA國際化得咁落力無非就係因為本土唔夠MLB同NFL黎囉</blockquote><br />\n雖然係咁講<br />\n但係NBA做咗咩令到佢國際化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n國際轉播嗰啲MLB同NFL都有</blockquote><br />\n主要係比人早做<br />\n飲左頭啖湯<br />\n其他地區唔多清楚<br />\n但以大陸為例<br />\n早期佢係貼錢請CCTV叫人去做直播<br />\n加埋NBA個種造星文化係幾搶眼<br />\n仲要正正係開始國際化正好係MJ巓峰時期<br />\n仲有92年夢之隊個D<br />\n效果自然事半功倍"},{"pid":"ca0a2c09caaec4941d39d3290da8d06398366126","tid":57721,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"因為其他無人玩law.<br />\n無份玩你點推廣都唔燃睇架La."},{"pid":"e97622ac89b1ca0228a173f546fdf78835146fe0","tid":57721,"uid":25126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"籃球場佔地少 可以周圍起<br />\nd人易接觸咪普及囉"},{"pid":"09753986b3174c08ff9c81055870994b521a9b2f","tid":57721,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有得嘆冷氣阿麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冰上曲棍球夠冷氣未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太凍，唔岩藍球撚玩"},{"pid":"5104b6feb515a158e37644533b841fc9cad0f37f","tid":57721,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩具多人玩係正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講呢個？ 我小朋友時都有玩過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/www.mypacetravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/2013-08-27-20.57.30-1.jpg?resize=700%2C519\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.mypacetravel.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F08%2F2013-08-27-20.57.30-1.jpg%3Fresize%3D700%252C519&h=73de6e88&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩具黎講藍波係好挽過足球機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62960b916f8e0ae5c9301f5069fb94ccb0d9743d","tid":57721,"uid":44925,"like":